<a name="8">[8]</a> <a href="#8" id=8>From the evolution construction and social construction point of views [Zhuge, 2012], tags might have been used in some texts by people.</a>
<a name="9">[9]</a> <a href="#9" id=9>Humans are specialized in recognizing pictures as they experience and reflect the physical space and form knowledge in mind.</a>
<a name="10">[10]</a> <a href="#10" id=10>One advantage of incorporating pictures into summary is that pictures provide a different bridge between language units (e.g., sentences), especially when connection sentence cannot be found in original text.</a>
